'''科特·克勞森'''（Curt Clawson；{{bd|1959年|9月28日}}）是[[美國|美國]]的一位政治人物。自2014年至2017年，他是[[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]第19選舉區選出的美國眾議院議員。他的黨籍是[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]。克勞森從政前是一位商人<ref name="naples">{{cite news | url=http://www.naplesnews.com/business/exclusive-curt-clawson-business-record-congress-19 | title=NDN exclusive: Curt Clawson touts business acumen, but record is marred | work=Naples Daily News | date=12 March 2014 | accessdate=27 July 2014 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150406171558/http://www.naplesnews.com/business/exclusive-curt-clawson-business-record-congress-19 | archive-date=2015-04-06 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last= |first= |date=April 22, 2014 |title=Ex-C.E.O. Wins Florida Primary for House Seat |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/04/23/us/politics/ex-ceo-wins-florida-primary-for-house-seat.html |newspaper=New York Times |location=New York City |publisher=New York Times Company |accessdate=April 23, 2014 |archive-date=2021-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314184722/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/04/23/us/politics/ex-ceo-wins-florida-primary-for-house-seat.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

